It is a JSON Schema (draft-06) of the Solidity compiler's compact JSON AST,
unioning solc versions >= 0.6: fields added in later solc releases are optional,
fields whose value can be null are anyOf-nullable.

To refresh: pick an explicit version and run
  curl -sL https://unpkg.com/solidity-ast@<version>/schema.json -o schema.json
then update this NOTICE and re-run tests/solidity_ast/ (the conformance test
will point at any model fields that need to follow).
